---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="道教文化 - 道奎">
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-tao-gold text-center mb-12">道教文化</h1>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- 道家思想 -->
      <a href="/dao/jiaoxue" class="block bg-tao-gray/50 border border-tao-gold/20 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-tao-gold/50 transition-all gold-glow group">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-tao-gold mb-3 group-hover:text-tao-red transition-colors">道家思想</h2>
        <p class="text-tao-light/70">老子、庄子、列子等道家经典思想，道法自然，无为而治。</p>
      </a>
      
      <!-- 三清四御 -->
      <a href="/dao/sanqing" class="block bg-tao-gray/50 border border-tao-gold/20 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-tao-gold/50 transition-all gold-glow group">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-tao-gold mb-3 group-hover:text-tao-red transition-colors">三清四御</h2>
        <p class="text-tao-light/70">道教最高神明体系：三清道祖、玉皇四御。</p>
      </a>
      
      <!-- 宫观道场 -->
      <a href="/dao/gongguan" class="block bg-tao-gray/50 border border-tao-gold/20 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-tao-gold/50 transition-all gold-glow group">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-tao-gold mb-3 group-hover:text-tao-red transition-colors">宫观道场</h2>
        <p class="text-tao-light/70">龙虎山、武当山、青城山等道教名山与宫观。</p>
      </a>
      
      <!-- 经籍典籍 -->
      <a href="/dao/jingji" class="block bg-tao-gray/50 border border-tao-gold/20 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-tao-gold/50 transition-all gold-glow group">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-tao-gold mb-3 group-hover:text-tao-red transition-colors">经籍典籍</h2>
        <p class="text-tao-light/70">《道德经》、《南华经》、《道藏》等道教经典。</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
